{"tid":1029810,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聯合醫院送柑打氣又甘又霉　前線醫護斥最毒祝福","createTime":"2019-02-20T13:34:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-21T10:05:15.000Z","uid":39464,"like":436,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":80,"replies":[{"pid":"92bec34b71e0e76662bd760110398c78ae14b478","tid":1029810,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T13:34:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190220/photo/bkn-20190220175602192-0220_00822_001_03b.jpg?20190220182531\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190220%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190220175602192-0220_00822_001_03b.jpg%3F20190220182531&h=7dcd3f7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190220/photo/bkn-20190220175602192-0220_00822_001_01b.jpg?20190220182531\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190220%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190220175602192-0220_00822_001_01b.jpg%3F20190220182531&h=a4f6f373&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n流感高峰期仍未過，前線醫護每日工作忙過不停，聯合醫院昨日(19日)向前線同事送柑打氣，卻竟已經發霉，演變成公關災難。有聯合醫院前線護士向東網形容，院方送上最毒的祝福，「即係我要做到好『甘』」並批評院方不夠誠意，進一步打擊前線士氣。<br />\n<br />\n聯合醫院昨日準備了一箱箱的生果，計劃向每間病房的前線醫護送上柑橘，基督教聯合醫務協會趁着新春給同事們送上生果表達謝意，並祝他們身體健康，生活愉快。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，院方送贈柑橘，同事紛紛表現不悅，除送柑的意頭不好，而且很多柑都已經發霉，不能食用，前線護士批評：「上次送過一次，嗰個星期已經好X柑，今次仲要送霉！」<br />\n<br />\n聯合醫院回覆指，基督教聯合醫務協會每年農曆新年期間，都會向醫院全體同事派送生果，以答謝同事過去一年的付出。生果供應商於2月18日將生果送到該院後，院方隨即於翌日(19日)安排向各同事派送。醫院其後接到同事反映部分生果的品質有問題，出現發霉或損壞等情況，即時為同事安排更換，並即時向供應商投訴及反映生果品質問題，供應商稍後會安排更換有問題的生果。院方就生果出現品質問題而對同事造成不便，向受影響的同事致歉。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190220/bkn-20190220175602192-0220_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190220%2Fbkn-20190220175602192-0220_00822_001.html&d=WIvcVJ42Qixy%2BOT8%2FM1n87PGlnsopddeS9pLw%2Bq5tFI%3D&h=380abbb8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190220/bkn-20190220175602192-0220_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"fad6d9dded2e01bce63177ed4870e600bad15abc","tid":1029810,"uid":39628,"like":257,"dislike":5,"score":252,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T13:35:27.000Z","msg":"食飽好上路<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25e2ebd35eac253bd410f6bf8315debf680c47ec","tid":1029810,"uid":26333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fad6d9dded2e01bce63177ed4870e600bad15abc","tid":1029810,"uid":39628,"like":257,"dislike":5,"score":252,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T13:35:27.000Z","msg":"食飽好上路<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T13:36:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"003515df070f6a9de766c2a056159bd828548c32","tid":1029810,"uid":190540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T13:37:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e727f2eb4bd199dbd9d9298da80d5a300fabf316","tid":1029810,"uid":36178,"like":262,"dislike":0,"score":262,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T13:38:11.000Z","msg":"唔撚係掛, 咁on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲衰過醫院餐隻非洲橙<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fa9f6dd7c7900bc028588cc43f0f0fc1857566e","tid":1029810,"uid":5490,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T13:38:33.000Z","msg":"痴線爛晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d09688407ec3e4cadf8569f0d93e5f67bf7b308c","tid":1029810,"uid":228963,"like":3,"dislike":72,"score":-69,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T13:38:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c5d004535907cefcfaa76151882f370a0b6aa764","tid":1029810,"uid":3122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy